script tag should always be at the last of the body elements or it can be placed
inside a head element but with a defer attribute.

<script src="" defer></script>

is html elements case-sensitive or case-insensitive ? Answer - case-insensitive
-
<div></div>
or <DIV></DIV>

example of case-sensitive - div, Div, DiV, diV, DIv But we have to use lowercase
- use
<div>
  instead of <DIV></DIV> we can create our own custom html elements(React,
  angular) <Login></Login>

  //types of css usages //inline, internal, external inline
  <div style="width: 100%; background-color: red">
    <p>This is a para</p>
    <button onclick="login()" id="login-btn">Login</button>
  </div>

  internal
  <style>
    div {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: red;
    }
  </style>

  external will create a file and then we use it - we create a different file
  for css and then we use it witl link tag
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="index.css" />
</div>

-------- BEM (Block Element Modifier)

<body>
  <div class="login-container">
    <p class="login-container_label">Enter your login details</p>
    <input type="text" class="login-container__text" />
    <button class="login-container__login--btn">Login here</button>
  </div>
</body>

--- Design approaches (Mobile-first approach, Desktop-first approach) we design
all these approaches using responsive design layout using flexbox, media
queries. ----- what is a box model ? Every element on the html will be converted
into a rectangular box what will be inside this rectangular box - - content -
padding - border - margin (this will separate html elements) what is the width
of an element ? content width + padding-right + padding-left + border-left +
border-right ------------------------------------- ---positioning -static
-relative -absolute -fixed
